Unified scorer:
- Remove routing wall in universal_predictor.predict(): all _compute_*
  functions now run unconditionally and self-zero when inputs absent.
  Metal entries now correctly accumulate non-covalent terms for cross-modal
  systems (metal@macrocycle, chalcogenide cages, etc.).
- Wire _compute_metal_terms to scorer_frozen.predict_log_k (replaces
  phantom metal_physics stub); handles cross-modal translational correction.
- Add _compute_cross_modal_ion_dipole() [Phase 12]: ion-dipole attraction
  for metal ion inside macrocyclic host (Rekharsky & Inoue 1998 calibration).
- Add _compute_portal_size_match() [Phase 13]: Gaussian size-match penalty
  for CB[n]/crown ether portal selectivity (Barrow 2015 calibration).

Non-carbon-bias donor expansion (core/noncarbonbias_donors.py):
- Se, Te, As, Sb, F, C donors; extended N/O/S variants.
  All parameters from Pearson 1988 HSAB, NIST SRD 46 back-solve,
  Ibers & Holm 1980, Marcus 1997, Cotton & Wilkinson.
- 13 new metals: Ru2+/3+, Os2+, Rh3+, Ir3+, Mo3+, W4+, Re3+,
  Tc2+, Ge2+, Zr4+, Hf4+, Ti4+, Be2+.

physics_realization_bridge.py:
- 8 new material systems in _MATERIAL_DONOR_DEFAULTS.
- Full periodic table fallback in _resolve_donor_subtypes.

